{"tid":2499412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港騙徒手法整合post，睇完唔好再中招","createTime":"2021-04-22T01:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T18:08:47.000Z","uid":74908,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"882f25b4aa43990d004c342d0f6b169197e65f49","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"騙徒手法層出不窮，香港人太多天真好心人<br />\n每隔段時間就有受害人年經月經post講自己被人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上得兩登多嘅人都知道係邊款騙徒<br />\n但都有唔少人未見過<br />\n希望一齊整理一份騙徒list方便了解騙徒生態<br />\n唔好再被呃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049c8c579213b2cd50cbf08719629e3139f5a1de","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><ins><span class=\"red\">不幸外國人</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：聲稱非常不幸被人偷/跌銀包，冇晒錢可唔可以幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時會周圍去求路人做好心<br />\n坐低路邊，只靠一塊紙皮黑色箱頭筆寫住自己「不幸」經歷都見過<br />\n<br />\n外貌：鬼佬，backpacker裝扮多<br />\n<br />\n出現地點：樓主佐敦，尖沙咀同旺角都見過<br />\n應該遊客區多<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：單人出現，私底下應該團隊運作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSSJbcce9nnhU8f9iuNHRbZjCcYb2CVhuvQciforCQRd9?filename=j5y7PNf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5y7PNf.jpg&h=1070ad4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aee5ca2a6a7b304c98a2b366e664e6f4a61714e0","tid":2499412,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e851192a045433203956dcf4b5b7b84eba31dd9","tid":2499412,"uid":335883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23cb64e05a892c0f00676101f942c06fe174147d","tid":2499412,"uid":70786,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"<ins>林鄭月娥</ins><br />\n叫人上大灣區投資，市民出事俾人呃走投無路投訴無門<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b175382ccef1898e9719ba085c8568ec1787ea","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:44:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><ins><span class=\"red\">是日本人Eddie</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：職業千變萬化嘅「日本人」，但又會有英文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身份呢次係大學教授下次可以係designer<br />\n一開始會問點搭去機場，之後就會好緊張講呢個方法唔夠時間去機場點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返飛的一個方法但幾百蚊車費身上唔夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n引受害者借錢後，會好有報恩心<br />\n留各種聯絡方式例如電話號碼 whatsapp,email等等<br />\n聲稱一定會還ali加多<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外貌：樓主未見過，但見有人影低過<br />\n<br />\n出現地點：遊客區<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：Eddie咁出名全港得你一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUc5jrbqktNDYjJHR4fNeNZoDpSYi7ysYaghMXVJoFcek?filename=pQhsPV8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQhsPV8.jpg&h=cc273111&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e84b7b1162f97f44a65b0fcfe5d1f550bb5dbbc2","tid":2499412,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279f9a75c949a58464bedda897568f997e355d1d","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><ins>假聾啞人</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：扮聾啞人士，識手語可以撚返佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手持小朋友都唔要嘅垃圾玩具/公仔/筆記簿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍向人以極度唔合理價格兜售，身上掛住一個證件套show俾人睇<br />\n「我係聾啞人士，請好心支持xx協會blablabla」<br />\n每件垃圾貨物都有價錢牌，派傳單咁強行塞俾人<br />\n唔願意買或者唔夠錢，就會惡死捉住人強迫要買/出夠錢，而且不設找續<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應付方法：要夠惡過對方千祈唔可以要<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外貌：衣着單易樸素，部分個樣似弱智人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出現地點：各區都有<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：多數2,3位出現，有人會扮義工輔助<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdLLYTfHeybPbEZW3rpX3Cdd35dut6ywteQffoDLoGRqb?filename=yiD0qOO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiD0qOO.jpg&h=6bf31dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPv8qfu2mLTBnjgsUY9pncvhtJdetWk3ZZiRgUF6Nv7jS?filename=eVvJ719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVvJ719.png&h=5f45d5d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1640dbe2ba88f3a1ea36b32eb3b95bc5704bb00c","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人接手可以講講大規模嘅層壓式推銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登最多人中都係呢樣"},{"pid":"7f7f1b769f6c88d9397838bc5b18a231d6f818f5","tid":2499412,"uid":100985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:54:17.000Z","msg":"樓主圖文講解幾有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，幫推"},{"pid":"416d1b93087a0ffca563207a37b43554e96baee7","tid":2499412,"uid":59920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反疫苗撚<br />\n叫人唔好打敗康tec<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己衝去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bec1da7c033ca16a92a3e9632f6fb40a32639e1","tid":2499412,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bus.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6499e9f6874252631143f5ad76384453dbacdf99","tid":2499412,"uid":158727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T03:17:42.000Z","msg":"gchi"},{"pid":"af9047c5d58a64658c182ce89a7818b4f3d5fe66","tid":2499412,"uid":234788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"樓主佛心POST幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beea1fa79745f6c44f125603c2eba63c3cb6b159","tid":2499412,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T03:44:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5eede2d3fe768ab9a607626ebc3a95029fe19a95","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><ins><span class=\"red\">健身狗</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：以上司強迫OT, 差最後一次可以收工為理由，專登向身形唔健康肥人瘦人落手<br />\n求受害者幫幫手玩抽獎刮刮卡/填問券/收傳單等等<br />\n會好熱情拖人手捉去附近間gym, 話有免費試玩送，填少少個人資料同度高磅重就ok<br />\n<br />\n職員會不停話你身體好唔健康，一次試堂唔夠<br />\n開始瘋狂疲勞轟炸sell人要其他plan，身邊仲有其他大隻佬行來行去俾壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咩定力就隨時玩完不知不覺簽貴價合約<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到受害者後悔就會威脅已經白紙黑字簽晒約，係咪想毀約先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應付方法：隨時都可以離開唔好驚，樓主都玩過一次，口渴飲幾杯免費水大大聲講明<strong><span class=\"x-large\">唔要！</span></strong>拍拍蘿友走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外貌：香港大型連鎖健身中心制服，正常人識認到<br />\n<br />\n出現地點：間gym樓下條街，邊區都有<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：拉客1個，上去間gym大量<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRoskApXeQEZC9AL1Sg7UkuhMj4djgUPCZXAi9uyDit3s?filename=ABTLCkq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABTLCkq.jpg&h=7cb75e30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23cab0314feca472b2ef7bb5e8ec67a0374b1e84","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"反應唔係幾好，平時唔係好多苦主咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d299d7ace19cf716e4674eeaa843a2ae0300e54","tid":2499412,"uid":287829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"支持你！"},{"pid":"5a2883a0e975e352671524e74a759df02b7bdbe8","tid":2499412,"uid":66283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"層壓式同電話電子騙案最多，樓主啲情況真係唔多人中"},{"pid":"adfef6a99b2fcaebcd13e2378a5f66b6ad56ceb8","tid":2499412,"uid":396535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"支持支持"},{"pid":"9c0b69e571cf2cf425a4f9dcc89ab2280aa5969d","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a2883a0e975e352671524e74a759df02b7bdbe8","tid":2499412,"uid":66283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"層壓式同電話電子騙案最多，樓主啲情況真係唔多人中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"以上年經都好多人中<br />\n今朝先見完中日本人騙案苦主post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電話騙案順豐香港人唔會點中，支那先會中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而假網店買限量波鞋玩具switch都想講"},{"pid":"7983954b090a1f3fb445c2b1a8ac98e384c5ccaf","tid":2499412,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"支那閪問人買野食"},{"pid":"2f30a1aba2d13e111becb5ad29eb99e50fcdd2d4","tid":2499412,"uid":46271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:24:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"576616427fa29b9e7bb445c7a2a61d5fceac000d","tid":2499412,"uid":346280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f371f4474922df728babe86e0d5014ecc2f19b32","tid":249941