:297152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:39:15.000Z","msg":"行騙係最仆街嘅人類罪行，唔只令人損失金錢甚至畢生積蓄，更可能對受害者造成永久心靈創傷，從此對人失去信任同善心，令整個社會都變得狡詐冷漠。"},{"pid":"f96f2861bae321cc0d94fecded44fe3f011b074b","tid":2499412,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"Eddie應該好多人撞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf3e94db076f95cbdfe0cfc47b110671d61e96d","tid":2499412,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"279f9a75c949a58464bedda897568f997e355d1d","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><ins>假聾啞人</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：扮聾啞人士，識手語可以撚返佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手持小朋友都唔要嘅垃圾玩具/公仔/筆記簿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍向人以極度唔合理價格兜售，身上掛住一個證件套show俾人睇<br />\n「我係聾啞人士，請好心支持xx協會blablabla」<br />\n每件垃圾貨物都有價錢牌，派傳單咁強行塞俾人<br />\n唔願意買或者唔夠錢，就會惡死捉住人強迫要買/出夠錢，而且不設找續<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應付方法：要夠惡過對方千祈唔可以要<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外貌：衣着單易樸素，部分個樣似弱智人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出現地點：各區都有<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：多數2,3位出現，有人會扮義工輔助<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiD0qOO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiD0qOO.jpg&h=6bf31dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVvJ719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVvJ719.png&h=5f45d5d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"呢個遇過<br />\n直頭上門塞垃圾比我叫我出價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aed5b45542cf07bf7d87f8e57a9e640c3ca381d","tid":2499412,"uid":7828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span class=\"green\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=bfdd3880\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=4cdffe03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=458d323b\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n最近好似搬咗去旺角恒利中心13-14樓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY5ER9dZh8AGSSyjQqeMDJpJYk8tLcWtoyzyKHDyCMcnY?filename=FXuxBB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXuxBB7.png&h=dffa07b7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYCUVLjCiM9o6GMnb9eUWZzL2V97XWsY8xP7t9STu61oe?filename=8Zcs5yn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Zcs5yn.png&h=acceb362&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88f0e55729b0b275ca608b3b0eea27519fd2e963","tid":2499412,"uid":7828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你可以聽下d錄音，有佢哋點呃人嘅手法<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZQSqbcJuxfRvLjUBfjdYJpimK45Wio66m9sc4YvKPvyH?filename=3uBd2Ja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uBd2Ja.png&h=5fe1a552&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVBpeyvNuGGykmUeMgffcKNokkVoRvJkrtRgVJG4J54Ff?filename=8cMOhAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cMOhAV.jpg&h=0de4aa7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbchYKXcaJMrevDm7eS5WmN68ZHQjN7FqcEDA2hbfqDUf?filename=QTyg7Fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTyg7Fc.jpg&h=9f46bf9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個騙徒係大陸人，由汕尾移民落黎香港，專呃d DSE 學生去報冇資歷級別 (HKQF) 嘅課程，另外會呃女性去美容院 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">更多資訊： </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3D62kedb7g&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=b0397a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3Di4waqbjt&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=83a5fe4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt</a> <br />\n<br />\n除咗美容，仲有SELL 教育，中醫，脫毛，投資等等<br />\n<br />\nChampion Team 另一成員 <br />\n如果去見工會見到佢 <br />\n(與Sam Chau Wing Sum 周詠森，Hugo Wong 及 三金合作） <br />\n<br />\n行業：教育及美容傳銷 <br />\n花名：Crystal Li / 水晶梨 <br />\n中文全名：李婉瑩 <br />\n英文全名：Li Wan Ying <br />\n<span class=\"red\">常用工作電話：91570141（Updated) <br />\n另一工作電話：51610763 (可以 iMessage) </span><br />\n<br />\n以下係佢部分冇p圖嘅真樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT7i9kibx9hRew9Nmp6si38in3Bkxryr6UxzDr2LaThLR?filename=O5DLuR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5DLuR6.jpg&h=b894d392&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ2R9QpUNnUcYtjrHTsHzXUoDDjfuVeCaBUtJWQyQYUiw?filename=yOkHOCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOkHOCZ.jpg&h=f279000e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQFtXt2uYWpPc7t1CjxMZQdD7VQqroNHBgHXWw6Mnwibs?filename=3mSK1X0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mSK1X0.jpg&h=be2c20d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX9oygEShcTVvpQbeppbEeZ4cCsJraYtBavaiF9m31rZC?filename=y2eHEUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2eHEUF.jpg&h=057c40bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係條女部分聲音 Backup <br />\n<br />\n同人plan 升學路線? <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-24\" data-sr-url