Time":"2021-04-22T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f790557c8cb2f93627122b2e6b4dd60727c69a","tid":2499412,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"玩極端啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩善良大愛利用人地善良大愛玩極端<br />\n有日大白鯊都會食素等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3b7cb676c1ae7a6a151cc8e201bce57f26ad16","tid":2499412,"uid":22893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"279f9a75c949a58464bedda897568f997e355d1d","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><ins>假聾啞人</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：扮聾啞人士，識手語可以撚返佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手持小朋友都唔要嘅垃圾玩具/公仔/筆記簿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍向人以極度唔合理價格兜售，身上掛住一個證件套show俾人睇<br />\n「我係聾啞人士，請好心支持xx協會blablabla」<br />\n每件垃圾貨物都有價錢牌，派傳單咁強行塞俾人<br />\n唔願意買或者唔夠錢，就會惡死捉住人強迫要買/出夠錢，而且不設找續<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應付方法：要夠惡過對方千祈唔可以要<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外貌：衣着單易樸素，部分個樣似弱智人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出現地點：各區都有<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：多數2,3位出現，有人會扮義工輔助<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiD0qOO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiD0qOO.jpg&h=6bf31dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVvJ719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVvJ719.png&h=5f45d5d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"試過行街同人傾傾下計塞落我手，我又不其言接左以為傳單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後佢追住我拎錢，諗住算鳩數俾10蚊佢，佢俾牌我睇話八十，我即刻屌左出聲塞番俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後推黎推去，最後我掉撚左佢入垃圾桶行左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66626b12362efeb6f778c0a2540b1ed9ed7554cc","tid":2499412,"uid":388788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23cb64e05a892c0f00676101f942c06fe174147d","tid":2499412,"uid":70786,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"<ins>林鄭月娥</ins><br />\n叫人上大灣區投資，市民出事俾人呃走投無路投訴無門<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a9aca3a7a624e8c2873e8a4315f9a63c6c0dc7","tid":2499412,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7680a9649066daaa4714cee5504612327b8ee59a","tid":2499412,"uid":187267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"中環放工過馬路日日叫人捐錢個個女人係唔係騙徒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"太子大廈輪椅狗都日撚日住正門口"},{"pid":"ca3cf2f960b459ab106ef8c13bf01fcb091f052b","tid":2499412,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}